and the wind slammed the door shut.

584
00:26:42,072 --> 00:26:43,113
I didn't bring my phone,

585
00:26:43,393 --> 00:26:44,953
so I borrowed the security's motorbike

586
00:26:44,953 --> 00:26:47,153
to go to Shen Qing's office
for the keys.

587
00:26:47,673 --> 00:26:49,032
I fell on the way back.

588
00:26:49,633 --> 00:26:50,792
Haste makes waste.

589
00:26:51,953 --> 00:26:52,833
The spare keys

590
00:26:52,888 --> 00:26:54,266
are hanging right behind the door.

591
00:26:54,777 --> 00:26:56,550
Why did you have to go through
all the trouble?

592
00:26:56,552 --> 00:26:58,193
Lian Jin was home.

593
00:27:00,232 --> 00:27:01,512
Someone was home?

594
00:27:02,193 --> 00:27:03,752
I was banging on the door,

595
00:27:03,752 --> 00:27:04,913
and no one answered.

596
00:27:05,393 --> 00:27:06,913
Gosh, this boy.

597
00:27:07,312 --> 00:27:08,032
I'm so sorry.

598
00:27:08,312 --> 00:27:09,752
Maybe he's just too shy

599
00:27:09,752 --> 00:27:10,953
to open the door.

600
00:27:10,953 --> 00:27:12,393
People upstairs heard me.

601
00:27:12,393 --> 00:27:13,512
Did he ignore me on purpose?

602
00:27:14,673 --> 00:27:15,193
You...

603
00:27:15,512 --> 00:27:17,113
Why would he do that?

604
00:27:17,272 --> 00:27:19,673
Maybe he was out at the time, right?

605
00:27:21,913 --> 00:27:22,873
You can't blame him.

606
00:27:22,873 --> 00:27:24,873
You need to think ahead.

607
00:27:25,377 --> 00:27:27,590
If you had taken the keys,
would this have happened?

608
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:28,800
I just went to throw the trash.

609
00:27:28,866 --> 00:27:31,155
It's your mistake. Don't blame others.

610
00:27:31,913 --> 00:27:32,153
I...

611
00:27:34,353 --> 00:27:36,353
Fine, it's my problem.

612
00:27:36,433 --> 00:27:36,953
Fine.

613
00:27:37,155 --> 00:27:38,600
- My problem.
- I'm truly sorry.

614
00:27:38,644 --> 00:27:39,549
Are you okay?

615
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,377
Are you hurt?

616
00:27:42,633 --> 00:27:43,433
Does it hurt...?

617
00:27:48,618 --> 00:27:49,312
Lina.

618
00:27:51,752 --> 00:27:52,153
Coming.

619
00:27:54,913 --> 00:27:55,312
Dad.

620
00:27:56,113 --> 00:27:56,953
Dinner is ready.

621
00:27:57,032 --> 00:27:59,393
Call Shen Qing and Duole over.

622
00:27:59,913 --> 00:28:01,149
Duole has a study hall.

623
00:28:01,150 --> 00:28:02,288
I'll pick him up after I eat.

624
00:28:02,355 --> 00:28:03,488
Shen Qing's still at work.

625
00:28:03,577 --> 00:28:04,466
Come over then.

626
00:28:04,488 --> 00:28:05,933
The dishes are ready.

627
00:28:06,422 --> 00:28:07,622
Eat them while they're hot.

628
00:28:08,992 --> 00:28:09,512
Come, Lina.

629
00:28:10,032 --> 00:28:10,913
This is fresh.

630
00:28:10,955 --> 00:28:12,088
Thank you, Ms. Lian.

631
00:28:19,032 --> 00:28:19,272
Come.

632
00:28:22,752 --> 00:28:23,312
Here, Lina.

633
00:28:23,866 --> 00:28:24,790
Thank you, Ms. Lian.

634
00:28:24,833 --> 00:28:25,593
Very fresh.

635
00:28:34,433 --> 00:28:34,833
Lian Jin,

636
00:28:36,873 --> 00:28:38,072
sit here.

637
00:28:38,953 --> 00:28:40,393
You can eat more.

638
00:28:44,992 --> 00:28:45,712
Don't mind him.

639
00:28:47,913 --> 00:28:48,673
He's like this.

640
00:28:49,712 --> 00:28:50,913
He has a habit

641
00:28:51,593 --> 00:28:53,353
of eating while reading.

642
00:28:53,472 --> 00:28:54,193
I spoiled him.

643
00:28:55,977 --> 00:28:57,111
He's got many bad habits.

644
00:29:01,792 --> 00:29:02,272
You're home.

645
00:29:02,873 --> 00:29:03,593
Dad, Ms. Lian.

646
00:29:03,888 --> 00:29:05,250
- You're back.
- Sit down and eat.

647
00:29:05,311 --> 00:29:06,430
I'll get you a bowl of rice.

648
00:29:06,430 --> 00:29:07,488
No need, I'll get it myself.

649
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:08,755
- Sit.
- Let Ms. Lian do it.

650
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:09,555
Sit down and eat.

651
00:29:09,910 --> 00:29:11,022
You've been working all day.

652
00:29:27,312 --> 00:29:30,272
I... I bought a non-stick spoon.

653
00:29:30,472 --> 00:29:31,752
I'll get you that.

654
00:29:32,232 --> 00:29:32,512
Come.

655
00:29:33,153 --> 00:29:34,072
I've put it here.

656
00:29:37,310 --> 00:29:39,866
How did the signing event go?

657
00:29:42,870 --> 00:29:44,066
What's wrong with you?

658
00:29:45,032 --> 00:29:46,353
Do you have no sense?

659
00:29:46,633 --> 00:29:48,552
Couldn't you give me a heads-up
before coming?

660
00:29:49,113 --> 00:29:50,232
I called you,

661
00:29:50,393 --> 00:29:51,953
but you didn't answer.

662
00:29:52,633 --> 00:29:53,709
If I didn't answer,

663
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:55,400
you thought it was okay to barge in?

664
00:29:57,072 --> 00:29:58,113
Didn't I tell you that?

665
00:29:58,153 --> 00:29:59,673
I was cooking chicken soup.

666
00:29:59,673 --> 00:30:00,833
I was anxious.

667
00:30:01,688 --> 00:30:03,044
Also, you told me not to call you

668
00:30:03,066 --> 00:30:04,288
if nothing serious happened.

669
00:30:04,311 --> 00:30:05,533
Even if you had answered,

670
00:30:05,577 --> 00:30:07,222
would you have brought me the keys?

671
00:30:08,593 --> 00:30:09,673
You messed up the event.

672
00:30:09,673 --> 00:30:10,792
Didn't I tell you

673
00:30:10,792 --> 00:30:12,232
this event was important?

674
00:30:12,393 --> 00:30:13,913
I prepared for it for a long time.

675
00:30:14,032 --> 00:30:15,353
Yet you just barged in.

676
00:30:17,113 --> 00:30:18,552
How was I supposed to know that?

677
00:30:19,393 --> 00:30:20,752
You don't tell me anything anymore.

678
00:30:20,866 --> 00:30:21,950
You didn't answer my calls.

679
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:24,155
How was I supposed to know
what you were busy with?

680
00:30:24,288 --> 00:30:26,644
Besides, I've had that lock for so long.

681
00:30:26,644 --> 00:30:27,710
I told you to install it.

682
00:30:27,712 --> 00:30:29,593
You keep pushing it off.

683
00:30:29,733 --> 00:30:31,050
Do you really care about our home?

684
00:30:31,153 --> 00:30:32,552
Didn't I say I'd do it this weekend?

685
00:30:32,622 --> 00:30:34,355
It's not like
I've been slouching around.

686
00:30:34,377 --> 00:30:36,000
Can't you do it yourself?

687
00:30:36,155 --> 00:30:38,022
If I knew how,
I would've done it already.

688
00:30:38,153 --> 00:30:39,032
Then learn!

689
00:30:39,032 --> 00:30:40,272
Never stop learning.

690
00:30:41,353 --> 00:30:42,752
You're not working, though.

691
00:30:42,752 --> 00:30:43,953
Can't you use your brain

692
00:30:43,953 --> 00:30:45,512
and figure something out?

693
00:30:46,393 --> 00:30:47,512
Unbothered.

694
00:30:47,512 --> 00:30:48,752
I'm not working?

695
00:30:48,873 --> 00:30:50,913
Having arguments is
a kind of communication.

696
00:30:51,193 --> 00:30:53,272
Your mom was sick, and Duole
had to go to school.

697
00:30:54,833 --> 00:30:56,472
I had to take care of both of them.

698
00:30:56,992 --> 00:30:58,312
You go on business trips

699
00:30:58,512 --> 00:30:59,873
or stay out whenever you want.

700
00:31:00,312 --> 00:31:02,312
I had to handle everything on my own.

701
00:31:02,377 --> 00:31:03,880
Do you remember
what you said back then?

702
00:31:03,888 --> 00:31:06,709
You were grateful I sacrificed my career
to support this family.

703
00:31:06,710 --> 00:31:08,222
And now you're saying I don't work

704
00:31:08,244 --> 00:31:08,870
and do nothing?

705
00:31:08,873 --> 00:31:09,552
When did I...

706
00:31:09,590 --> 00:31:11,288
Shen Qing, you can't do this to me.

707
00:31:12,673 --> 00:31:13,749
"Never stop learning"?

708
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:15,288
Oh, I can learn a bunch of things.

709
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:16,955
I can learn to change locks. What else?

710
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,844
Learn acupuncture skills, foot baths,

711
00:31:18,953 --> 00:31:20,272
and CPR like Ms. Lian does?

712
00:31:21,353 --> 00:31:22,593
This is getting out of hand.

713
00:31:23,593 --> 00:31:23,913
Right.

714
00:31:23,992 --> 00:31:25,072
She's talking out of turn.

715
00:31:25,844 --> 00:31:27,244
Liu Lina, you're going too far.

716
00:31:27,866 --> 00:31:28,750
I'm going too far?

717
00:31:28,844 --> 00:31:31,177
The one who didn't open the door for me
went way too far.

718
00:31:32,833 --> 00:31:33,712
What?

719
00:31:33,933 --> 00:31:35,666
Who didn't open the door for you?

720
00:31:36,552 --> 00:31:36,913
Him!

721
00:31:37,488 --> 00:31:38,990
He was home but didn't let me in.

722
00:31:40,288 --> 00:31:42,422
I yelled so loud. There's no way
he didn't hear me.

723
00:31:42,833 --> 00:31:43,873
I almost broke the door.

724
00:31:47,113 --> 00:31:47,673
Well,

725
00:31:48,873 --> 00:31:49,312
Shen Qing.

726
00:31:50,266 --> 00:31:51,111
Here's the rice.

727
00:31:53,752 --> 00:31:54,312
Let's eat.

728
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,470
This is how things are at home.

729
00:31:58,393 --> 00:31:58,873
Well.

730
00:32:00,232 --> 00:32:00,992
Lina

731
00:32:01,177 --> 00:32:02,470
takes care of the whole family.

732
00:32:02,472 --> 00:32:04,272
She's also helping us.

733
00:32:04,512 --> 00:32:05,913
We all see that.

734
00:32:08,552 --> 00:32:09,153
Shen Qing,

735
00:32:10,193 --> 00:32:11,433
you need to be fair.

736
00:32:12,032 --> 00:32:13,232
You're working outside

737
00:32:13,992 --> 00:32:15,472
to provide for the family.

738
00:32:16,873 --> 00:32:18,633
Lina is doing the same thing.

739
00:32:19,190 --> 00:32:20,866
She's also contributing to the family.

740
00:32:21,593 --> 00:32:22,833
A family works that way.

741
00:32:23,193 --> 00:32:24,633
You both have different roles,

742
00:32:25,312 --> 00:32:25,712
right?

743
00:32:26,433 --> 00:32:27,673
It's not necessary

744
00:32:28,552 --> 00:32:30,633
to fight over a lock.

745
00:32:31,193 --> 00:32:33,153
Just change it.

746
00:32:33,312 --> 00:32:35,312
Smart locks are pretty convenient.

747
00:32:35,673 --> 00:32:37,232
Dad, ask him.

748
00:32:37,232 --> 00:32:39,312
How many times have I told him?

749
00:32:39,633 --> 00:32:41,353
Your door has been replaced,

750
00:32:41,353 --> 00:32:43,353
but my smart lock is still sitting
in its box.

751
00:32:43,353 --> 00:32:44,109
Enough.

752
00:32:44,110 --> 00:32:45,266
If the lock had been changed,

753
00:32:45,311 --> 00:32:46,733
none of this would've happened.

754
00:32:47,032 --> 00:32:48,433
Can you show some respect?

755
00:32:55,512 --> 00:32:55,792
Mom,

756
00:32:56,353 --> 00:32:57,113
I miss you.

757
00:32:57,666 --> 00:32:58,310
Since you left,

758
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,333
there's no one in this family
to keep things fair.

759
00:33:00,833 --> 00:33:01,953
Lina, calm down.

760
00:33:01,953 --> 00:33:02,953
- Wait, no.
- Dad.

761
00:33:02,992 --> 00:33:04,869
Why is she talking
about your mother now?

762
00:33:04,870 --> 00:33:05,511
It's not that.

763
00:33:05,712 --> 00:33:05,992
No...

764
00:33:06,193 --> 00:33:08,593
She's mad at me.

765
00:33:10,633 --> 00:33:11,953
This is getting complicated.

766
00:33:13,022 --> 00:33:13,910
She's just mad at me.

767
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:16,022
Unbelievable.

768
00:33:33,272 --> 00:33:35,193
Dad, can you really do this?

769
00:33:36,833 --> 00:33:37,873
Do you want to do it then?

770
00:33:38,232 --> 00:33:40,113
You can practice your handyman skills.

771
00:33:40,673 --> 00:33:41,272
Shen Duole,

772
00:33:41,488 --> 00:33:43,111
do you want me to take you there?

773
00:33:43,472 --> 00:33:44,312
Dad, good luck.

774
00:33:44,312 --> 00:33:45,433
I'm off. Bye.

775
00:33:57,792 --> 00:33:58,113
Dad.

776
00:33:58,270 --> 00:33:59,088
You're working on it.

777
00:33:59,992 --> 00:34:01,712
That's the right attitude.

778
00:34:05,222 --> 00:34:06,600
Are you sure you can handle this?

779
00:34:06,833 --> 00:34:07,472
If not,

780
00:34:07,472 --> 00:34:09,072
I can ask the guy who set up my bed

781
00:34:09,072 --> 00:34:09,672
to come over.

782
00:34:09,711 --> 00:34:11,222
He said he knows how to install locks.

783
00:34:11,233 --> 00:34:12,072
No need. It's simple.

784
00:34:12,072 --> 00:34:13,032
There's a manual here.

785
00:34:13,032 --> 00:34:13,873
I'll follow it.

786
00:34:13,873 --> 00:34:14,552
Right.

787
00:34:14,622 --> 00:34:16,190
Are you going for a walk with Ms. Lian?

788
00:34:16,222 --> 00:34:17,533
We're heading out to buy groceries.

789
00:34:17,666 --> 00:34:18,177
Be careful.

790
00:34:18,866 --> 00:34:19,550
No need to help?

791
00:34:19,552 --> 00:34:20,353
Don't worry.

792
00:34:20,873 --> 00:34:21,512
I'm leaving.

793
00:34:21,873 --> 00:34:22,713
Be careful, Dad.

794
00:34:23,270 --> 00:34:24,200
Take care, Ms. Lian.

795
00:34:40,870 --> 00:34:41,911
Yes, Mr. Wei?

796
00:34:43,353 --> 00:34:43,992
All right.

797
00:34:44,192 --> 00:34:45,949
Two hours.

798
00:34:45,950 --> 00:34:47,244
I'll send it to you in two hours.

799
00:35:09,753 --> 00:35:10,313
Jin,

800
00:35:10,873 --> 00:35:13,632
did you find someone to fix

801
00:35:13,632 --> 00:35:15,353
the broken lock on the office door?

802
00:35:16,552 --> 00:35:18,672
Can you call that guy again

803
00:35:18,672 --> 00:35:20,793
to install a biometric lock for me?

804
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:23,555
The sooner, the better.

805
00:35:25,873 --> 00:35:26,192
Okay.

806
00:35:33,233 --> 00:35:34,393
It's good that you're back.

807
00:35:37,433 --> 00:35:38,433
Your husband went out.

808
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:46,088
Come record your fingerprint.

809
00:35:46,632 --> 00:35:47,793
Do you know who I am

810
00:35:47,793 --> 00:35:48,913
before asking that?

811
00:35:48,913 --> 00:35:50,112
What if I'm the mistress?

812
00:35:50,472 --> 00:35:51,192
No way.

813
00:35:51,592 --> 00:35:52,833
No mistress looks like you.

814
00:35:56,152 --> 00:35:56,753
What do I do?

815
00:35:57,032 --> 00:35:57,393
Here.

816
00:35:57,670 --> 00:35:58,666
Press your thumb here.

817
00:36:02,793 --> 00:36:03,072
Wait.

818
00:36:03,672 --> 00:36:05,233
This isn't the lock I bought.

819
00:36:05,833 --> 00:36:07,672
Your husband bought it at my shop.

820
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:08,688
Installation is included.

821
00:36:11,072 --> 00:36:12,072
What's going on?

822
00:36:24,592 --> 00:36:25,592
How much is this?

823
00:36:26,733 --> 00:36:27,350
Not expensive.

824
00:36:27,430 --> 00:36:28,333
I gave him a discount.

825
00:36:28,353 --> 00:36:29,152
3,880 yuan.

826
00:36:31,233 --> 00:36:32,512
3,880 yuan?

827
00:36:33,873 --> 00:36:34,913
Can I return it?

828
00:36:35,393 --> 00:36:36,152
No.

829
00:36:36,433 --> 00:36:37,472
It's already installed.

830
00:36:41,233 --> 00:36:41,953
Ma'am,

831
00:36:41,953 --> 00:36:43,592
are you not happy with my service?

832
00:36:46,353 --> 00:36:46,992
No, it's fine.

833
00:36:47,913 --> 00:36:48,713
You can go now.

834
00:36:48,844 --> 00:36:49,350
All right.

835
00:37:07,672 --> 00:37:08,672
One moment.

836
00:37:15,393 --> 00:37:15,873
See?

837
00:37:16,273 --> 00:37:17,152
It's done.

838
00:37:19,873 --> 00:37:22,152
Shen Qing gets things done fast.

839
00:37:22,793 --> 00:37:23,512
Just like you.

840
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:29,733
I love that compliment.

841
00:37:31,112 --> 00:37:32,112
Mr. Li, playing chess?

842
00:37:32,433 --> 00:37:33,233
You're back, Lina.

843
00:37:33,233 --> 00:37:34,152
Who's winning?

844
00:37:34,632 --> 00:37:35,072
Mister.

845
00:37:35,072 --> 00:37:36,552
It's Li. He won.

846
00:37:36,713 --> 00:37:37,112
Good.

847
00:37:37,511 --> 00:37:38,310
You're back, Lina.

848
00:37:48,273 --> 00:37:49,592
Is it salty?

849
00:37:49,873 --> 00:37:50,313
No.

850
00:37:50,822 --> 00:37:52,400
It's not comfortable sitting like this.

851
00:37:52,422 --> 00:37:52,952
Come.

852
00:37:52,953 --> 00:37:54,713
Get up.

853
00:37:54,713 --> 00:37:56,152
Lean on this.

854
00:37:56,753 --> 00:37:57,233
Lie down.

855
00:37:58,433 --> 00:37:58,833
Done.

856
00:37:59,533 --> 00:38:01,190
When daughters go back to their parents,

857
00:38:01,192 --> 00:38:02,353
they

858
00:38:02,833 --> 00:38:04,032
bring a check in the left hand

859
00:38:04,244 --> 00:38:05,470
and a duck in the right hand.

860
00:38:05,753 --> 00:38:06,472
But you?

861
00:38:06,873 --> 00:38:08,233
You brought back a stupid lock.

862
00:38:08,992 --> 00:38:10,592
You think we're a junkyard

863
00:38:10,913 --> 00:38:12,793
for useless trash from your house?

864
00:38:13,512 --> 00:38:14,552
I told you

865
00:38:14,552 --> 00:38:15,592
we bought two locks.

866
00:38:16,433 --> 00:38:17,472
It's not a stupid lock.

867
00:38:17,632 --> 00:38:18,672
It's over 2,000 yuan.

868
00:38:22,753 --> 00:38:24,273
Look around.

869
00:38:24,273 --> 00:38:24,953
Look closer.

870
00:38:25,793 --> 00:38:27,472
What here is worth 2,000 yuan?

871
00:38:29,313 --> 00:38:29,953
You see.

872
00:38:30,632 --> 00:38:31,032
Done?

873
00:38:31,152 --> 00:38:32,873
Smart locks are convenient.

874
00:38:33,313 --> 00:38:35,072
Of course. It costs 2,000, after all.

875
00:38:35,353 --> 00:38:36,313
It better be.

876
00:38:36,672 --> 00:38:37,233
Let me see.

877
00:38:43,233 --> 00:38:44,632
If you pay me 2,000 yuan,

878
00:38:45,592 --> 00:38:47,273
I'll sit by the door all day

879
00:38:47,632 --> 00:38:49,233
and open and close it

880
00:38:49,233 --> 00:38:50,112
for you.

881
00:38:50,552 --> 00:38:51,753
I can even sing.

882
00:38:51,873 --> 00:38:52,393
Good idea.

883
00:38:53,032 --> 00:38:54,313
My pension is over around 4,000.

884
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:55,311
Go ahead and sing.

885
00:38:55,433 --> 00:38:58,353
What a beautiful jasmine flower.

886
00:38:58,873 --> 00:38:59,632
Welcome home.

887
00:39:00,433 --> 00:39:02,953
What a beautiful jasmine flower.

888
00:39:03,152 --> 00:39:03,833
Welcome home.

889
00:39:05,233 --> 00:39:06,793
Not bad.

890
00:39:08,592 --> 00:39:09,552
All right.

891
00:39:09,552 --> 00:39:11,192
Stop eating. Get moving.

892
00:39:11,192 --> 00:39:12,152
It's time to go home.

893
00:39:12,310 --> 00:39:13,911
If I go home, I have to open the door.

894
00:39:14,472 --> 00:39:15,552
That makes me mad.

895
00:39:16,833 --> 00:39:18,632
Getting mad twice if I go home,

896
00:39:18,992 --> 00:39:19,353
so no.

897
00:39:19,592 --> 00:39:20,672
No?

898
00:39:20,913 --> 00:39:22,273
Isn't Shen Qing eating dinner?

899
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:23,755
Let him starve.

900
00:39:24,288 --> 00:39:26,488
He's a grown man.
If he could starve to death so easily,

901
00:39:26,533 --> 00:39:27,355
then leave him be.

902
00:39:46,511 --> 00:39:49,555
(Mr. Shen, this is the investment plan.)

903
00:39:53,444 --> 00:40:00,577
(Okay. Thanks a lot.)

904
00:40:16,552 --> 00:40:18,512
(The city at night is dazzling.)

905
00:40:19,133 --> 00:40:20,666
(Go for a run after working overtime)

906
00:40:20,913 --> 00:40:22,393
(and get ready for tomorrow.)

907
00:40:53,112 --> 00:40:54,472
Honestly, when I think about it,

908
00:40:54,472 --> 00:40:55,393
it's Lian Jin's fault.

909
00:40:56,355 --> 00:40:58,430
He was home
but didn't open the door for Lina.

910
00:40:58,552 --> 00:41:00,353
That's why they fought.

911
00:41:01,353 --> 00:41:02,552
Sometimes, his personality

912
00:41:02,552 --> 00:41:04,233
can be really frustrating.

913
00:41:07,672 --> 00:41:09,273
It's been two days.

914
00:41:09,433 --> 00:41:11,233
Haven't you gotten over it yet?

915
00:41:11,433 --> 00:41:12,273
I just think...

916
00:41:12,273 --> 00:41:13,273
No, listen.

917
00:41:13,273 --> 00:41:14,112
Listen.

918
00:41:14,313 --> 00:41:15,672
That's Lina.

919
00:41:16,592 --> 00:41:17,992
She's outspoken.

920
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,355
One good thing about her is

921
00:41:19,355 --> 00:41:20,977
that she doesn't hold grudges.

922
00:41:21,873 --> 00:41:22,672
I know.

923
00:41:23,066 --> 00:41:25,488
Also, can you blame others
for a couple's bickering?

924
00:41:25,533 --> 00:41:27,150
What couple doesn't argue?

925
00:41:27,793 --> 00:41:28,869
Don't take it to heart.

926
00:41:28,870 --> 00:41:29,777
Don't think that way.

927
00:41:29,790 --> 00:41:31,022
If you keep thinking like this,

928
00:41:31,433 --> 00:41:33,112
