929
00:41:35,672 --> 00:41:36,953
You always help him.

930
00:41:38,592 --> 00:41:38,953
Jeez.

931
00:41:43,953 --> 00:41:44,393
Lian Jin.

932
00:41:46,632 --> 00:41:47,713
Heading to shower?

933
00:41:49,032 --> 00:41:51,393
Want me to turn up the water temperature

934
00:41:51,873 --> 00:41:52,552
by two degrees?

935
00:41:53,313 --> 00:41:54,472
Hot water feels better.

936
00:41:56,192 --> 00:41:56,592
No need.

937
00:42:01,112 --> 00:42:01,753
Oh, right.

938
00:42:02,353 --> 00:42:02,833
Say,

939
00:42:04,433 --> 00:42:05,472
we ran out of shampoo.

940
00:42:05,666 --> 00:42:07,888
I bought a new bottle
but forgot to put it back.

941
00:42:08,270 --> 00:42:09,133
It's right here.

942
00:42:11,244 --> 00:42:12,088
Here you go.

943
00:42:12,753 --> 00:42:13,192
Use this.

944
00:42:20,152 --> 00:42:21,992
I have a lecture this weekend.

945
00:42:22,433 --> 00:42:23,873
Do you want to join your mom

946
00:42:24,472 --> 00:42:25,472
and cheer me on?

947
00:42:28,310 --> 00:42:29,244
- Sure.
- I...

948
00:42:29,313 --> 00:42:29,592
Good.

949
00:42:29,822 --> 00:42:30,777
It's a good opportunity

950
00:42:30,913 --> 00:42:31,753
for you to explore.

951
00:42:32,688 --> 00:42:33,270
That's great.

952
00:42:37,713 --> 00:42:38,793
You need to wake up early.

953
00:42:44,032 --> 00:42:44,433
Thank you.

954
00:42:55,592 --> 00:42:56,192
It's fine.

955
00:42:56,844 --> 00:42:57,550
He's just a boy.

